snippet.title: Pounce Update Trailer - Path of Titans
snippet.description:
Prepare yourself for the Pounce Update...

This isn’t just an update, it’s an evolution. Enter the test of your cunning, agility, and adaptability as a dinosaur.

Meet the Eurhinosaurus, the new Ichthyosaur and real-life leviathan from 180 million years ago. Take the controls of a creature from the depths of the sea with fierce teeth to compete against the Sarcosuchus, Spinosaurus and Kaiwhekea.
